        "collapse_KraMpf": {
          "type": "collapse",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>How do I start dosing?</p>",
            "content": "<p>Start low and go slow. Begin with the smallest listed serving for 2–3 days, take notes on focus, mood, and energy, then adjust gradually if needed. Change one thing at a time, avoid late‑day stimulants, and stop or reduce if you feel unwanted effects. If you use <a href=\"/collections/racetams\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Racetams\">racetams</a>, consider pairing a choline source (e.g., <a href=\"/products/alpha-gpc-250mg-capsules\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Alpha-GPC 250mg Capsules\">Alpha‑GPC</a> or <a href=\"/products/cdp-choline-250mg-capsules\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"CDP-choline 250mg Capsules\">Citicoline</a>). This isn’t medical advice—talk to your clinician if you have any conditions or take medication.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapse_TjyHYb": {
          "type": "collapse",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>What if it’s not for me?</p>",
            "content": "<p>Unopened items are returnable—see our <a href=\"/pages/shipping-and-returns\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shipping & Returns Policy\">easy‑returns policy</a>.</p>"
